    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Incompatible with other conversions</em></p>\n<p>You modify your lightweapon, causing it to eminate a sickly green light. Your modified lightsaber loses the luminous property.</p>\n<p>Additionally, when you make your first attack on your turn, you can alter the properties of your modified lightsaber. Until the start of your next turn, the damage type of your modified lightsaber is changed to acid.</p>\n<p>You can use this trait a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (a minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you complete a short or long rest.</p>",
